<TEXT>
COMPAGNIE Generale des Eaux (CGE) has been confirmed as the successful
bidder for the huge Universum-Film Babelsberg studios at Potsdam, outside
Berlin. It beat Bertelsmann, the German media group.
The supervisory board of the Treuhand privatisation agency confirmed the
